// lint-staged config (lives inline under "lint-staged" in package.json).
//
// The whole local gate: fast type-check on staged TypeScript. No ESLint, no
// Prettier - that is deliberate (CodeRabbit profile is `chill`; the gate is
// tsc + jscpd + this hook). See guides/13-jscpd-and-quality-gate.md.
{
  "*.ts": [
    "bash -c 'tsc --noEmit --skipLibCheck'"
  ],
  "*.md": []
}
